== 1.2.0

* Monkey-patch the git gem to support submodule commits when running git
  ls-tree in repositories, until the pull request is merged.


== 1.1.0

* Ignore copies of external libraries when counting contributions.
* Add number of commits in a given language to the output.
* Add lines changed by month to the output.
* Relicense under the MIT license.


== 1.0.1

* Fix variable type.


== 1.0.0

* Support determining more file languages based on file content.
* Add tally of commits by weekday and hour.
* Skip symlinks and submodule references when parsing commits.
* Handle more parsing exceptions when determining the language of the file.
* Standardized key names in JSON output.


== 0.1.0

* Initial version.
